    "However, systems such as Retrieval Augmented Models (RAGs) can use both parametric-memory (to leverage their own knowledge like GPT) and non-parametric memory (to extract data from external knowledge bases).",
    "Such design benefits various forms of question-answering systems by reducing hallucinations (Hu et al., 2023).",
    "Our system could thus be evaluated on RAGs by using the evidence-base from white papers and other official sources as external knowledge bases.",
